GETTING AIRBORNE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GLIDER FLIGHTS 
</P>
<P>
Who: Sky Sailing 
</P>
<P>
Calls: 782-0404 
</P>
<P>
Where: Warner Springs Airport 
</P>
<P>
When: 9 a.m. to sunset, Monday through Friday. 
</P>
<P>
Cost: One-person scenic and introductory flights, 20 to 40 minutes long, are 
$48 to $93; flights for two, 20 to 40 minutes long, over No Name, Hot Springs 
or Palomar Mountain, are $68 to $138, or $34 to $69 per person. 
</P>
<P>
Notes: Reservations required for weekdays and flights after 5 p.m. 
</P>
