Photo, Motion and Emotion: Recess at summer school finds delighted youngsters 
exploring all the elements at Central Park in Pasadena. Otto Deleon wafts 
clusters of wobbling bubbles into the air, and Jose Manuel -- they're both 6 -- 
sees how far water from the fountain can go toward cooling a guy. Meanwhile, a 
