Beathard in order to earn an invitation to Charger camp . . . Photos by DAVID 
McNEW / Los Angeles Times; Photo, John Carney is said to be the "cleanest" 
kicker . . . Fuad Reveiz hopes to follow through on career that began 
promisingly in Miami. 
</P>
