<TEXT>
<P>
Parkland appropriation -- The Times incorrectly reported Wednesday that the $12 
million a House subcommittee included in legislation to buy parkland in the 
Santa Monica Mountains National Recreation Area is the largest appropriation 
the park has ever received. It would match the highest figure since 1985. 
</P>
