for killing . . . SCOTT ANGER; Photo, . . . teen-age gang member David 
Dominguez, below. ; Photo, Billy Joe McIlvain. as he appeared in the 1970s, 
when he was a San Gabriel police officer. ; Photo, BILLY JOE McILWAIN, 
